         Vector2D position,
         java.lang.String name)
        Creates a copy of an existing shape - Set parameter corresponding to the original shape
        Parameters:
        list - list of vertices of the shape, same for copy
        position - position of the original shape also as position for the copy (update with mouse position)
        name - Name of the original shape will be modified with a "Copy" string before
